msgstr ""
"Onderdak voor je mensen. Je kunt er ook je goederen en gereedschap opslaan."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans warehouse: Headquarters
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1340 input:1340
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "The headquarters is your main building."
msgstr "Het hoofdkwartier is je belangrijkste gebouw."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans warehouse: Port
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1347
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1354 input:1347
#: input:1354 standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Serves as a base for overseas colonization and trade. Also stores your "
"soldiers, wares and tools."
msgstr ""
"Dient als basis voor overzeese kolonisatie en handel. Hier kun je ook je "
"soldaten, goederen en gereedschappen opslaan."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans market: Market
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1362 input:1362
#: standard
